    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "交锋对垒哪见老",
        "吴班",
        "报子",
        "某十岁弓马全习好",
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士引吴班同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉旨出川把贼扫，\n开路先行不辞劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄老将军到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。黄忠上，下马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先锋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军怒气不息，为着谁来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先锋！想那关兴、张苞，乃子侄之辇，在阵前擒来谭雄，不过是些小小的功劳。\n主公在酒席筵前，夸之不已，反道昔年五虎上将，俱都老迈无用。是我单人\n独骑，怒出御营，要到东吴盘营，生擒孙权，活捉潘璋，刀劈他几员上将，看\n我老是不老！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那关兴、张苞，本是少年英雄，莫怪主公称赞。据末将看来，你本来的是老\n了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "却为何人人道我老！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由我怒火往上烧。\n十三四岁学宝刀；\n数十载未离马鞍鞒。\n到如今八十三岁不服老，我是哪些儿老？"
        },
        {
          "character": "某十岁弓马全习好、交锋对垒哪见老、吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本来是老了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "岂惧那东吴的小儿曹。\n来来来带过爷的“追风豹”——"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "斩几个人头你们瞧一瞧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄忠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这老将人老心不老，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴班",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我暗地保护走一遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
