    {
      "scene_index": 9,
      "label": "第九场",
      "characters_present": [
        "临危再把主公劝",
        "关兴",
        "况且仇人两相见",
        "刘备",
        "大丈夫战死终难免",
        "大喝潘璋休弄险",
        "平吴之后太平宴",
        "幸得全尸已无怨",
        "张苞",
        "急忙低头谢恩典",
        "报子",
        "臣爱主公恩非浅",
        "黄忠"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士引刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤王筵前言失检，\n激怒了老将去争先。\n但愿平安早回还。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关兴、张苞扶黄忠同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见老将身带箭，\n朕心如落百丈渊。\n早知出兵遭此险……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "悔不该一时错出言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮小导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮小导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "精神恍惚四肢软，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳旁听得有人言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看刀！哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "原来陛下在眼前。\n只恐性命难保全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大喝潘璋休弄险、急忙低头谢恩典、刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤一言之错，激怒老将军出营，如今带箭而归，怎不教孤痛断肝肠！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀主公啊！老臣出得御营，就刀劈了崔禹、史蹟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就该回营才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！臣见潘璋，手使二千岁的青龙偃月刀，只气得我肝胆裂碎，正要擒捉那贼，\n不想却被冷箭射中肩窝！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军乃是百步穿杨之手，为何不防？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，陛下呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老臣智不如王翦，\n临阵岂肯不当先！\n匆忙哪顾听弓弦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "况且仇人两相见、刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "况且仇人两相见、刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "真乃风云不测变，\n令人血泪洒胸前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备向张苞、关兴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老将军中箭身受险，\n恨尔等保护不周全！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陛下！这是为臣自不小心，休要瞒怨二位小将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既已如此，待孤与老将军起箭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀陛下！这箭上有毒，箭在臣在，箭去臣亡！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军，此箭不起，敢是惧痛么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀！老臣死且不怕，岂能惧痛！但得苟延一时，与陛下一言永别耳。区区此\n心，伏乞圣听！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平生今洒泪几点，\n回首功名数十年。\n粉身碎骨理当然。\n叩谢龙恩归九泉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平吴不如取中原。"
        },
        {
          "character": "臣爱主公恩非浅、幸得全尸已无怨、临危再把主公劝、刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老将军休要心慌乱，\n去箭医伤未必难；\n孤愿你安宁寿百年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "平吴之后太平宴、黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "平吴之后太平宴、黄忠",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见主公说话泪满面，\n张苞、关兴哭两边。\n强打精神且留连。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大丈夫战死终难免、刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大丈夫战死终难免、刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "事到此间勿挽转，\n张苞、关兴听我言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大丈夫战死终难免、刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张苞、关兴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张苞、关兴",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扶住老将军，待孤与他起箭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！想我身为大将，这起箭何用搀扶，待臣自起。\n闪开了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄忠起箭，死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老将一死孤心好惨！\n冤仇未报恨难填。\n五虎上将三不见……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老将军哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不灭东吴誓不还！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将老将军尸首盛殓起来，送往成都！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘璋讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张苞、关兴，快快带领人马，与吴兵决一死战。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张苞、关兴",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
